{
  "text": "Taking into account the above facts and applying [CITATION_1] Lem. 3] , it can be proved the following result which shows that if the configuration of dicritical points of an arbitrary foliation F on P 2 is P-sufficient, then Algorithm 3 and Proposition 2 can be applied to decide whether F has a rational first integral (and to compute it).",
